net.sf.mmm.util.lang.base.datatype.adapter.jackson

Class DatatypeJsonSerializer<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.JsonSerializer<T>
      • net.sf.mmm.util.lang.base.datatype.adapter.jackson.DatatypeJsonSerializer<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - is the generic type of the Datatype to serialize.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.jsonFormatVisitors.JsonFormatVisitable

    public class DatatypeJsonSerializer<T>
extends com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.JsonSerializer<T>
    This is a generic JsonSerializer based on DatatypeDescriptorManager so every Datatype supported by DatatypeDescriptorManager can be serialized to JSON.
    Since:
    6.0.0
    Author:
    Joerg Hohwiller (hohwille at users.sourceforge.net)
    See Also:
    DatatypeJsonDeserializer
